title: Ep. 195 - Sex Abuse Crisis In The Southern Baptist Church
description:
Today on the show, a new report reveals the horrifying extent of the sex abuse crisis in the Southern Baptist church. We’ll discuss. Also, Alexandria Ocasio-Cortez is trying to backpedal and invent excuses for some of the insane stuff in her Green New Deal proposal, but the excuses are pathetic and dishonest. Date: 02-11-2019
